sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant MoMo as MoMo API
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Payment as Payment Service
    participant PaymentDB as Payment DB
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant OrderDB as Order DB

    Note over MoMo,GW: KH thanh toan tren app MoMo xong<br/>MoMo gui IPN den endpoint public - khong can auth
    MoMo->>GW: POST /api/payments/momo/ipn
    Note over MoMo,GW: orderId, requestId, amount<br/>resultCode, signature, transId

    GW->>Payment: Forward request - no auth required

    Payment->>Payment: Xac minh HMAC signature
    Note over Payment: HMAC-SHA256 voi secretKey<br/>rawSignature = accessKey + amount + extraData + ...

    alt Signature khong hop le
        Payment-->>MoMo: 400 - signature invalid
    else resultCode != 0 - Thanh toan that bai
        Payment->>PaymentDB: payment.findByProviderOrderId(orderId)
        Payment->>PaymentDB: payment.update - status=FAILED
        Payment-->>MoMo: 200 - nhan biet that bai
    else Signature hop le va resultCode = 0
        Payment->>PaymentDB: payment.findByProviderOrderId(orderId)
        PaymentDB-->>Payment: payment record - status=PENDING

        alt Payment da COMPLETED truoc do - tranh xu ly 2 lan
            Payment-->>MoMo: 200 - da xu ly
        else Payment chua xu ly
            Payment->>PaymentDB: paymentSession.create
            Note over Payment,PaymentDB: sessionType=MOMO_IPN<br/>transId, momoOrderId
            Payment->>PaymentDB: paymentTransaction.create
            Note over Payment,PaymentDB: amount, method=MOMO<br/>status=SUCCESS, transId
            Payment->>PaymentDB: payment.update - status=COMPLETED
            PaymentDB-->>Payment: payment da cap nhat

            Payment->>MQ: Publish payment_exchange / payment.completed
            Note over Payment,MQ: orderId, paymentId<br/>totalAmount, method=MOMO

            Payment-->>MoMo: 200 - xu ly thanh cong
        end
    end

    Note over MQ,OrderDB: Xu ly bat dong bo - Order Service consume

    MQ->>Order: Consume payment_exchange / payment.completed
    Order->>OrderDB: order.findByOrderId(orderId)
    Order->>OrderDB: order.update - status PENDING_PAYMENT -> PAID

